<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437874>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. Collected specimens. Gerromorpha, Hydrometridae. A. Hydrometra argentina, micropterous male from São Mateus, Espírito Santo (−18.7100, −39.7800). B. Hydrometra comata, micropterous male from Sooretama, Espírito Santo (−19.0269, −40.2276). C. Hydrometra fruhstorferi, apterous male from São Fidélis, Rio de Janeiro (−21.8330, −41.8298). D. Hydrometra sztolcmani, macropterous male from São José do Barreiro, São Paulo (−22.7263, −44.6276). Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437874/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437876>
    dc:description "FIGURE 25. Distribution of Hydrometra argentina (yellow), H. comata (pink), H. fruhstorferi (red) and H. sztolcmani (blue) in southeastern Brazil. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records; question marks indicate unspecified localities." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437876/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

